ansible Jenkins
===========
$ sudo usermod -s /bin/bash jenkins
$ sudo su - jenkins
$ ssh-keygen
enter

$ ssh-copy-id ec2-user@dockerprivateip
$ ssh ec2-user@dockerprivateip
logout
logout
$ sudo usermod -aG ec2-user Jenkins
$ sudo chmod -R g+rx /home/ec2-user

$ cd Ansible/
$ nano hosts.ini
[dockerhost]
dockerip ansible_user=ec2-user
$ cd 
$ sudo systemctl restart Jenkins

in the Jenkins page
create a new job
add source code management git
in the configure
=>post build steps
=>execute shell
ansible-playbook -i /home/ec2-user/Ansible/hosts.ini /home/ec2-user/Ansible/deploy-webapp.yaml
save and apply build
